    UserStatus
        Routes
            update_user_status()
                method: POST
                fields: string username, string status ("online" or "offline")
                return: jsonify({"message": string})
            get_user_status()
                method: GET
                fields: string username
                return: jsonify({"status": string})
        Tests
            test_update_and_get_user_status()
                creates a user, sets status to "online", then checks returned status
            test_update_status_for_nonexistent_user()
                attempts to update status for a non-existent user; checks status code
            test_update_status_to_offline()
                creates a user, sets to "online", then "offline", and verifies the final status

